 of your hide at every turn.  death penalty, racial xp penalty, class xp penalty, skill xp penalty, pet xp penalty are all geared to make sure you don't level either at all or nearly hardly ever.  THIS IS A LEVEL BASED GAME.  All their calculation put a HEAVY HEAVY HEAVY percentage on your level.  That's what the game is about.  I know it's bad programing or shall I be more specific, it is lazy, unimaginative programming, but that is the basis of their calculations for everything.  Any roll you can think of in the game is based on your level to a high high high degree.  With this in mind don't you know they will fight tooth and nail to keep you from leveling?
