s.  As a beastlord I fear we will miss alot of the balancing attnetion as we will get balanced as a melee, which we are, yet so dependant on our pet's that those fixes don't really help as much as they should.  Ancient spells won't happen for us either, so pet fixes are what I hope for.<P>I would also like to see mages and necros be thought of as something more than CoTH and corpse summon/mana batteries by the masses in raid situations.<P>If you read this far, thanks for listening to me babble.
